Worlds Finest (000 - 026 + Extra) (2012 - 2014) (Digital) (Nahga-Empire)


Starring Helena Wayne and Power Girl, two Earth-2 transplants stuck on the main earth of the DC Universe, Worlds' Finest is a "Second Wave" book of DC's The New 52 concept which follows the events of Paul Levitz's Huntress mini series and Mister Terrific, the cancelled series by Eric Wallace.

Written by:

Paul Levitz (#1 - Present)

Illustrated by:

George Perez (#1 - Present)

Kevin Maguire (#1 - Present)
